    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、貴方まだいたの？　相変わらず仕事の虫ね\n少しは休まないと体に悪いわよ",
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、莉央さんが忘れ物を取りに事務所に来るって\n葵から聞いたので、待っていたんです",
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "待っていた？　もしかして次のライブのこと？\n何か問題でもあったかしら",
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、琴乃から聞いてます。莉央さんが\n『星の海の記憶』を歌うことに躊躇してるって",
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その話\nそれなら、さっき琴乃にも言ったけど――",
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい！\n結論を出す前に俺の話を聞いてくれませんか？",
      "startTime": 39.4,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}